    <section name="Release Notes">
      <subsection name="6.0.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: TODO February 2020</p>
        <ul>
         <li>
            Upgrade to Bloomreach Experience Manager 14.<br/>
           <a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-335'>HIPFORGE-335</a>
           <br/>
           Rome library is upgraded to 1.12.0 version, package names are changed from <strong>com.sun</strong> to <strong>com.rometools</strong>.
           <br/>
           Please revisit the <a href="install.html">Installation page</a>.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="5.0.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 15 November 2019</p>
        <ul>
         <li>
            Upgrade to Bloomreach Experience Manager 13.<br/>
           This includes repackaging from <code>org.onehippo</code> to <code>org.bloomreach</code> and also the artifacts'
           Maven coordinates have changed likewise. Please revisit the <a href="install.html">Installation page</a>.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="4.0.1">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 3 August 2017</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Bump parent POM to use version 29 of project POM
          </li>
          <li>
            Demo: Fix HST configuration bootstrap resources and log4j configuration for local deployment.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="4.0.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 2 August 2017</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Upgrade to be CMS 12 compatible. The changes to the plugin (rather than the demo) are basically
            limited to converting the XML-based bootstrap resources to YAML format.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0.3">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 13 Februari 2017</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1432'>HIPPLUG-1432</a><br/>
            Prevent NullPointerException in case property 'feed:category' is not found on the feed descriptor document.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0.2">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 12 September 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1377'>HIPPLUG-1377</a><br/>
              Ability to exclude multiple document types
          </li>
          <li>Restart with -Drepo.bootstrap=true when upgrading to this release.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0.1">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 18 August 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href='https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPPLUG-1363'>HIPPLUG-1363</a><br/>
            Ability to set multiple document types
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="3.0.0">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 15 August 2016</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Compatible with Hippo CMS 11.0.</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
